This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with 3D human pose estimation from single images. The use of Convolutional Networks (ConvNets) also suggests that it could be classified under Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories. The paper also mentions the augmentation of popular datasets like LSP and MPII, which could indicate that it falls under Graphics (cs.GR) and Multimedia (cs.MM) categories.
